function selbox(props) {
    return <>
        <option>Select</option>
                                    <option value="Unit">{props.lData.bNo+"_"+props.lData.uNo}</option>
                                    <option value="Pool">props.lData</option>
                                    <option value="Post Box">Post Boxes</option>
                                    <option value="Gym Equipment">Gym Equipment</option>
                                    <option value="Club House">Club House</option>
    </>
}

export default selbox;
